# /{clubId}/agenda/{meetingNo}/{meetingId} → Expo baseUrl (see app.json experiments.baseUrl)
/:clubId/agenda/:meetingNo/:meetingId  /weblogin/:clubId/agenda/:meetingNo/:meetingId  302

# Short public agenda: /a/{meetingId}
/a/:meetingId  /weblogin/a/:meetingId  302

# Branded short agenda: /{club-slug}/a/{meetingId}
/:brand/a/:meetingId  /weblogin/:brand/a/:meetingId  302

